 filian 频道订阅人数突破200万，成为活跃英语VTuber史上第三人https://p2y.jp/filian-becomes-the-3rd-active-english-speaking-vtuber-in-history-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/ https://p2y.jp/filian-becomes-the-3rd-active-english-speaking-vtuber-in-history-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/#respondp2y_admin Thu, 13 Jul 2023 04:05:17 +0000 VTuberバーチャルfilianMythic TalentYouTubeYouTuberチャンネル登録者数(YouTube)バーチャルYouTuber https://p2y.jp/?p=96318 <p> VTuber filian（所属：Mythic Talent）是截至2023年7月13日（令和5年）目前活跃的第三位英语达人，拥有官方YouTube频道。</p>后<a href="https://p2y.jp/filian-becomes-the-3rd-active-english-speaking-vtuber-in-history-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/">filian 订阅者达到 200 万，成为英语世界第三位活跃 VTuber，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p>截至2023年7月13日，VTuber <strong>filian</strong> （所属：Mythic Talent）已实现200万YouTube官方频道订阅者，使他成为英语世界第三位活跃达人。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-attachment-id="96320" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/filian-becomes-the-3rd-active-english-speaking-vtuber-in-history-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023.jpg" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/filian_youtube_channel_14_july_2023.jpg" alt="filian 频道订阅人数突破200万，成为活跃英语VTuber史上第三人" class="wp-image-96320"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">菲莲<br>© 神话人才 2023</figcaption></figure><p>这是VTuber人才（包括现役、暂停、毕业、退役人才）中的第九人。 filian所属Mythic Talent的VTuber人才中，是本站认证的首个VTuber人才，也是Hololive Production以外200万人次的首创成果。这是自首次亮相以来816天的记录。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="2,000,000！！" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qWC83b3L6Vs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="hrhid64afcecb4e0c9" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
